    "These are the words of the covenant, which the LORD commanded <span class=\"person\">Moses</span> to make with the children of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> in the land of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>, beside the covenant which he made with them in <span class=\"place\">Horeb</span>.",
